<view class="page"><view class="hero-card"><view class="title">鲜花兑换中心</view><view class="subtitle">选择已盛开的花朵，填写收货信息后提交兑换订单</view></view><view class="card"><view class="card-title">可兑换花朵</view><view wx:if="{{a}}" class="empty"> 暂无可兑换花朵（需花朵进入盛开阶段且未兑换） </view><view wx:for="{{b}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:key="c" class="{{['flower-item', item.d && 'active']}}" bindtap="{{item.e}}"><view class="flower-name">{{item.a}}</view><view class="flower-meta">阶段：{{item.b}}</view></view></view><view class="card form-card"><view class="card-title">收货信息</view><view class="form-item"><view class="label">收货人</view><input class="input" placeholder="请输入收货人姓名" placeholder-class="input-placeholder" value="{{c}}" bindinput="{{d}}"/></view><view class="form-item"><view class="label">手机号</view><input class="input" type="number" maxlength="11" placeholder="请输入手机号" placeholder-class="input-placeholder" value="{{e}}" bindinput="{{f}}"/></view><view class="form-item"><view class="label">所在地区</view><input class="input" placeholder="如：广东省 深圳市 南山区" placeholder-class="input-placeholder" value="{{g}}" bindinput="{{h}}"/></view><view class="form-item"><view class="label">详细地址</view><block wx:if="{{r0}}"><textarea class="textarea" placeholder="请输入街道、门牌号等详细地址" placeholder-class="input-placeholder" value="{{i}}" bindinput="{{j}}"/></block></view><button class="submit-btn" disabled="{{l}}" bindtap="{{m}}">{{k}}</button></view></view>